{"tid":1801220,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"(煲底之約?)真實故事","createTime":"2019-12-28T12:40:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-28T12:52:05.000Z","uid":246353,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"051f94e2071b6b2990e636e3b06ac02427efb26a","tid":1801220,"uid":246353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T12:40:44.000Z","msg":"我唔會講件事既時間，地點，亦唔會有相或影片。因為要保護手足以免被起底。<br />\n<br />\n某日係遠離戰區既河邊散步<br />\n有對男女手拖手跑左過黎剛好停在我附近<br />\n黑衣黑褲黑鞋口罩<br />\n女既約155高 男既高佢一個頭有多<br />\n佢地黎個極速簡單換裝<br />\n我地個位冇cctv都算隱蔽既<br />\n口罩全程冇除過<br />\n換裝過後緊抱一起<br />\n仲情不自禁嘴起黎<br />\n但怪異既係佢地都係冇除口罩<br />\n但有摷野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n究竟佢地摷野係原自信任定不信任呢<br />\n佢地有冇見過對方真面目?<br />\n隱左聽到少少內容<br />\n知道女既得15歲<br />\n<br />\n畫面相當浪漫同詭異就連電影同動畫都未見過<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBtw 如果你地睇到既話<br />\n祝你地有情人終成眷屬啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"471059dc568d704f771db1a224096963e454c01e","tid":1801220,"uid":153679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T12:41:54.000Z","msg":"文章想表達既係。。。。。"},{"pid":"027ec45036f8d3d3e4c0b3032f5a8e6da2ec964d","tid":1801220,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T12:42:43.000Z","msg":"－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n投票： <a href=\"https://forms.gle/hDfcr3wCsprrvnC37\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FhDfcr3wCsprrvnC37&d=9uLtkTaOKuy%2FgkD%2BHbzoNUoInKkgZqzseva8eQDkMF8%3D&h=f9eff996\" target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/hDfcr3wCsprrvnC37</a><br />\n<br />\n【最後4日】全民票選十八區區議會主席與發言人－民主統戰部<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1800922\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1800922</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/phk5doO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fphk5doO.jpg&h=40b71bc8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n投票： <a href=\"https://forms.gle/hDfcr3wCsprrvnC37\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FhDfcr